The paper deals with the problem of aligning/matching two graphs, which is a fundamental problem in computer science. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as it deals with graph algorithms and their applications. The paper also involves network analysis and machine learning, which makes cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories.
